      <title>核监督机构说，特朗普在伊朗的下一步范围内迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/nuclear-watchdog-says-trump-looms-large-over-next-steps-in-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国核监管机构呼吁美国和伊朗开始谈判，这表明美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）采取了下一步行动，试图在其原子活动上与伊斯兰共和国的紧张局势进行抗辩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/nuclear-watchdog-says-trump-looms-large-over-next-steps-in-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 13:36:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
